<body>
<div type="acte" n="1">
                <head>LE GORA</head>
<div type="scene" n="1">
                    <head/>
<sp who="#bobechotte">
                        <speaker>BOBÉCHOTTE.</speaker>
                        <p n="1">
	<s n="1">Trognon, je vais bien t'épater. </s>
	<s n="2">Oui, je vais t'en boucher une surface. </s>
	<s n="3">Sais-tu qui est-ce qui m'a fait un cadeau ? </s>
	<s n="4">La concierge.</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="BOBÉCHOTTE"-->
<sp who="#gustave">
                        <speaker>GUSTAVE.</speaker>
                        <p n="2">
	<s n="1">Peste ! </s>
	<s n="2">Tu as de belles relations ! </s>
	<s n="3">Tu ne m'avais jamais dit ça !</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="GUSTAVE"-->
<sp who="#bobechotte">
                        <speaker>BOBÉCHOTTE.</speaker>
                        <p n="3">
	<s n="1">Ne chine pas la concierge, Trognon ; c'est une femme tout ce qu'il y a de bath ; à preuve qu'elle m'a donné... </s>
	<s n="2">– Devine quoi ? </s>
	<s n="3">- Un gora !</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="BOBÉCHOTTE"-->
<sp who="#gustave">
                        <speaker>GUSTAVE.</speaker>
                        <p n="4">
	<s n="1">La concierge t'a donné un gora ?</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="GUSTAVE"-->
<sp who="#bobechotte">
                        <speaker>BOBÉCHOTTE.</speaker>
                        <p n="5">
	<s n="1">Oui, mon vieux.</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="BOBÉCHOTTE"-->
<sp who="#gustave">
                        <speaker>GUSTAVE.</speaker>
                        <p n="6">
	<s n="1">Et qu'est-ce que c'est que ça, un gora ?</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="GUSTAVE"-->
<sp who="#bobechotte">
                        <speaker>BOBÉCHOTTE.</speaker>
                        <p n="7">
	<s n="1">Tu ne sais pas ce que c'est qu'un gora ?</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="BOBÉCHOTTE"-->
<sp who="#gustave">
                        <speaker>GUSTAVE.</speaker>
                        <p n="8">
	<s n="1">Ma foi, non.</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="GUSTAVE"-->
<sp who="#bobechotte">
                        <speaker>BOBÉCHOTTE, égayée.</speaker>
                        <p n="9">
	<s n="1">Mon pauvre Trognon, je te savais un peu poire, mais à ce point-là, je n'aurais pas cru. </s>
	<s n="2">Alors, non, tu ne sais pas qu'un gora, c'est un chat ?</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@stage="happy"--><!--@who="BOBÉCHOTTE"-->
<sp who="#gustave">
                        <speaker>GUSTAVE.</speaker>
                        <p n="10">
	<s n="1">Ah !... </s>
	<s n="2">Un angora, tu veux dire.</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="GUSTAVE"-->
<sp who="#bobechotte">
                        <speaker>BOBÉCHOTTE.</speaker>
                        <p n="11">
	<s n="1">Comment ?</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="BOBÉCHOTTE"-->
<sp who="#gustave">
                        <speaker>GUSTAVE.</speaker>
                        <p n="12">
	<s n="1">Tu dis : un gora.</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="GUSTAVE"-->
<sp who="#bobechotte">
                        <speaker>BOBÉCHOTTE.</speaker>
                        <p n="13">
	<s n="1">Naturellement, je dis : un gora.</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="BOBÉCHOTTE"-->
<sp who="#gustave">
                        <speaker>GUSTAVE.</speaker>
                        <p n="14">
	<s n="1">Eh bien, on ne dit pas : un gora.</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="GUSTAVE"-->
<sp who="#bobechotte">
                        <speaker>BOBÉCHOTTE.</speaker>
                        <p n="15">
	<s n="1">On ne dit pas : un gora ?</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="BOBÉCHOTTE"-->
<sp who="#gustave">
                        <speaker>GUSTAVE.</speaker>
                        <p n="16">
	<s n="1">Non.</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="GUSTAVE"-->
<sp who="#bobechotte">
                        <speaker>BOBÉCHOTTE.</speaker>
                        <p n="17">
	<s n="1">Qu'est-ce qu'on dit, alors ?</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="BOBÉCHOTTE"-->
<sp who="#gustave">
                        <speaker>GUSTAVE.</speaker>
                        <p n="18">
	<s n="1">On dit : un angora.</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="GUSTAVE"-->
<sp who="#bobechotte">
                        <speaker>BOBÉCHOTTE.</speaker>
                        <p n="19">
	<s n="1">Depuis quand ?</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="BOBÉCHOTTE"-->
<sp who="#gustave">
                        <speaker>GUSTAVE.</speaker>
                        <p n="20">
	<s n="1">Depuis toujours.</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="GUSTAVE"-->
<sp who="#bobechotte">
                        <speaker>BOBÉCHOTTE.</speaker>
                        <p n="21">
	<s n="1">Tu crois ?</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="BOBÉCHOTTE"-->
<sp who="#gustave">
                        <speaker>GUSTAVE.</speaker>
                        <p n="22">
	<s n="1">J'en suis même certain.</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="GUSTAVE"-->
<sp who="#bobechotte">
                        <speaker>BOBÉCHOTTE.</speaker>
                        <p n="23">
	<s n="1">J'avoue que tu m'étonnes un peu. </s>
	<s n="2">La concierge dit : un gora, et si elle dit : un gora, c'est qu'on doit dire : un gora. </s>
	<s n="3">Tu n'as pas besoin de rigoler ; je la connais mieux que toi, peut-être, et c'est encore pas toi, avec tes airs malins, qui lui feras le poil pour l'instruction.</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="BOBÉCHOTTE"-->
<sp who="#gustave">
                        <speaker>GUSTAVE.</speaker>
                        <p n="24">
	<s n="1">Elle est si instruite que ça ?</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="GUSTAVE"-->
<sp who="#bobechotte">
                        <speaker>BOBÉCHOTTE, avec une grande simplicité.</speaker>
                        <p n="25">
	<s n="1">Tout ce qui se passe dans la maison, c'est par elle que je l'ai appris.</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@stage="naive"--><!--@who="BOBÉCHOTTE"-->
<sp who="#gustave">
                        <speaker>GUSTAVE.</speaker>
                        <p n="26">
	<s n="1">C'est une raison, je le reconnais, mais ça ne change rien à l'affaire, et pour ce qui est de dire : un angora, sois sûre qu'on dit : un angora.</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="GUSTAVE"-->
<sp who="#bobechotte">
                        <speaker>BOBÉCHOTTE.</speaker>
                        <p n="27">
	<s n="1">Je dirai ce que tu voudras, Trognon ; ça m'est bien égal, après tout, et si nous n'avons jamais d'autre motif de discussion...</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="BOBÉCHOTTE"-->
<sp who="#gustave">
                        <speaker>GUSTAVE.</speaker>
                        <p n="28">
	<s n="1">C'est évident.</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="GUSTAVE"-->
<sp who="#bobechotte">
                        <speaker>BOBÉCHOTTE.</speaker>
                        <p n="29">
	<s n="1">N'est-ce pas ?</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="BOBÉCHOTTE"-->
<sp who="#gustave">
                        <speaker>GUSTAVE.</speaker>
                        <p n="30">
	<s n="1">Sans doute.</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="GUSTAVE"-->
<sp who="#bobechotte">
                        <speaker>BOBÉCHOTTE.</speaker>
                        <p n="31">
	<s n="1">Le tout, c'est qu'il soit joli, hein ?</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="BOBÉCHOTTE"-->
<sp who="#gustave">
                        <speaker>GUSTAVE.</speaker>
                        <p n="32">
	<s n="1">Qui ?</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="GUSTAVE"-->
<sp who="#bobechotte">
                        <speaker>BOBÉCHOTTE.</speaker>
                        <p n="33">
	<s n="1">Le petit nangora que m'a donné la concierge, et, à cet égard-là, il n'y a pas mieux. </s>
	<s n="2">Un vrai amour de petit nangora, figure-toi ; pas plus gros que mon poing, avec des souliers blancs, des yeux comme des cerises à l'eau-de-vie, et un bout de queue pointu, pointu, comme l'éteignoir de ma grand'mère... </s>
	<s n="3">Mon Dieu, quel beau petit nangora !</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="BOBÉCHOTTE"-->
<sp who="#gustave">
                        <speaker>GUSTAVE.</speaker>
                        <p n="34">
	<s n="1">Je vois, au portrait que tu m'en traces, qu'il doit être, en effet, très bien. </s>
	<s n="2">Une simple observation, mon loup ; on ne dit pas : un petit nangora.</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="GUSTAVE"-->
<sp who="#bobechotte">
                        <speaker>BOBÉCHOTTE.</speaker>
                        <p n="35">
	<s n="1">Tiens ? </s>
	<s n="2">Pourquoi donc ?</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="BOBÉCHOTTE"-->
<sp who="#gustave">
                        <speaker>GUSTAVE.</speaker>
                        <p n="36">
	<s n="1">Parce que c'est du français de cuisine.</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="GUSTAVE"-->
<sp who="#bobechotte">
                        <speaker>BOBÉCHOTTE.</speaker>
                        <p n="37">
	<s n="1">Eh ben, elle est bonne, celle-là ! </s>
	<s n="2">Je dis comme tu m'as dit de dire.</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="BOBÉCHOTTE"-->
<sp who="#gustave">
                        <speaker>GUSTAVE.</speaker>
                        <p n="38">
	<s n="1">Oh ! </s>
	<s n="2">Mais pas du tout ; je proteste. </s>
	<s n="3">Je t'ai dit de dire : un angora, mais pas : un petit nangora.</s>
</p>
                        <stage type="estonish">Muet étonnement de Bobéchotte.</stage>
                        <p n="39">
	<s n="1">C'est que, dans le premier cas, l'a du mot angora est précédé de la lettre N, tandis que c'est la lettre T qui précède, avec le mot petit ?</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="GUSTAVE"-->
<sp who="#bobechotte">
                        <speaker>BOBÉCHOTTE.</speaker>
                        <p n="40">
	<s n="1">Ah ?</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="BOBÉCHOTTE"-->
<sp who="#gustave">
                        <speaker>GUSTAVE.</speaker>
                        <p n="41">
	<s n="1">Oui.</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="GUSTAVE"-->
<sp who="#bobechotte">
                        <speaker>BOBÉCHOTTE, haussant les épaules.</speaker>
                        <p n="42">
	<s n="1">En voilà des histoires ! </s>
	<s n="2">Qu'est-ce que je dois dire, avec tout ça ?</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@stage="wave"--><!--@who="BOBÉCHOTTE"-->
<sp who="#gustave">
                        <speaker>GUSTAVE.</speaker>
                        <p n="43">
	<s n="1">Tu dois dire : un petit angora.</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="GUSTAVE"-->
<sp who="#bobechotte">
                        <speaker>BOBÉCHOTTE.</speaker>
                        <p n="44">
	<s n="1">C'est bien sûr, au moins ?</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="BOBÉCHOTTE"-->
<sp who="#gustave">
                        <speaker>GUSTAVE.</speaker>
                        <p n="45">
	<s n="1">N'en doute pas.</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="GUSTAVE"-->
<sp who="#bobechotte">
                        <speaker>BOBÉCHOTTE.</speaker>
                        <p n="46">
	<s n="1">Il n'y a pas d'erreur ?</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="BOBÉCHOTTE"-->
<sp who="#gustave">
                        <speaker>GUSTAVE.</speaker>
                        <p n="47">
	<s n="1">Sois tranquille.</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="GUSTAVE"-->
<sp who="#bobechotte">
                        <speaker>BOBÉCHOTTE.</speaker>
                        <p n="48">
	<s n="1">Je tiens à être fixée, tu comprends.</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="BOBÉCHOTTE"-->
<sp who="#gustave">
                        <speaker>GUSTAVE.</speaker>
                        <p n="49">
	<s n="1">Tu l'es comme avec une vis.</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="GUSTAVE"-->
<sp who="#bobechotte">
                        <speaker>BOBÉCHOTTE.</speaker>
                        <p n="50">
	<s n="1">N'en parlons plus. </s>
	<s n="2">Maintenant, je voudrais ton avis. </s>
	<s n="3">J'ai envie de l'appeler Zigoto.</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="BOBÉCHOTTE"-->
<sp who="#gustave">
                        <speaker>GUSTAVE.</speaker>
                        <p n="51">
	<s n="1">Excellente idée !</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="GUSTAVE"-->
<sp who="#bobechotte">
                        <speaker>BOBÉCHOTTE.</speaker>
                        <p n="52">
	<s n="1">Il me semble.</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="BOBÉCHOTTE"-->
<sp who="#gustave">
                        <speaker>GUSTAVE.</speaker>
                        <p n="53">
	<s n="1">Je trouve ça épatant !</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="GUSTAVE"-->
<sp who="#bobechotte">
                        <speaker>BOBÉCHOTTE.</speaker>
                        <p n="54">
	<s n="1">N'est-ce pas ?</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="BOBÉCHOTTE"-->
<sp who="#gustave">
                        <speaker>GUSTAVE.</speaker>
                        <p n="55">
	<s n="1">C'est simple.</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="GUSTAVE"-->
<sp who="#bobechotte">
                        <speaker>BOBÉCHOTTE.</speaker>
                        <p n="56">
	<s n="1">Gai.</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="BOBÉCHOTTE"-->
<sp who="#gustave">
                        <speaker>GUSTAVE.</speaker>
                        <p n="57">
	<s n="1">Sans prétention.</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="GUSTAVE"-->
<sp who="#bobechotte">
                        <speaker>BOBÉCHOTTE.</speaker>
                        <p n="58">
	<s n="1">C'est facile à se rappeler.</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="BOBÉCHOTTE"-->
<sp who="#gustave">
                        <speaker>GUSTAVE.</speaker>
                        <p n="59">
	<s n="1">Ça fait rire le monde.</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="GUSTAVE"-->
<sp who="#bobechotte">
                        <speaker>BOBÉCHOTTE.</speaker>
                        <p n="60">
	<s n="1">Et ça dit bien ce que ça veut dire. </s>
	<s n="2">Oui, je crois que pour un tangora, le nom n'est pas mal trouvé.</s>
</p>
                        <stage type="laugh">Elle rit.</stage>
                    </sp><!--@who="BOBÉCHOTTE"-->
<sp who="#gustave">
                        <speaker>GUSTAVE.</speaker>
                        <p n="61">
	<s n="1">Pour un quoi ?</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="GUSTAVE"-->
<sp who="#bobechotte">
                        <speaker>BOBÉCHOTTE.</speaker>
                        <p n="62">
	<s n="1">Pour un tangora.</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="BOBÉCHOTTE"-->
<sp who="#gustave">
                        <speaker>GUSTAVE.</speaker>
                        <p n="63">
	<s n="1">Ce n'est pas pour te dire des choses désagréables, mais ma pauvre cocotte en sucre, j'ai de la peine à me faire comprendre. </s>
	<s n="2">Fais donc attention, sapristoche ! </s>
	<s n="3">On ne dit pas : un tangora.</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="GUSTAVE"-->
<sp who="#bobechotte">
                        <speaker>BOBÉCHOTTE.</speaker>
                        <p n="64">
	<s n="1">Ça va durer longtemps, cette plaisanterie-là ?</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="BOBÉCHOTTE"-->
<sp who="#gustave">
                        <speaker>GUSTAVE, interloqué.</speaker>
                        <p n="65">
	<s n="1">Permets...</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@stage="estonish"--><!--@who="GUSTAVE"-->
<sp who="#bobechotte">
                        <speaker>BOBÉCHOTTE.</speaker>
                        <p n="66">
	<s n="1">Je n'aime pas beaucoup qu'on s'offre ma physionomie, et si tu es venu dans le but de te payer mon 24-30, il vaudrait mieux le dire tout de suite.</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="BOBÉCHOTTE"-->
<sp who="#gustave">
                        <speaker>GUSTAVE.</speaker>
                        <p n="67">
	<s n="1">Tu t'emballes ! tu as bien tort ! </s>
	<s n="2">Je dis : « On dit un angora, un petit angora ou un gros angora » ; il n'y a pas de quoi fouetter un chien, et tu ne vas pas te fâcher pour une question de liaison.</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="GUSTAVE"-->
<sp who="#bobechotte">
                        <speaker>BOBÉCHOTTE.</speaker>
                        <p n="58">
	<s n="1">Liaison !... </s>
	<s n="2">Une liaison comme la nôtre vaut mieux que bien des ménages, d'abord ; et puis, si ça ne te suffit pas, épouse-moi ; est-ce que je t'en empêche ? </s>
	<s n="3">Malappris ! </s>
	<s n="4">Grossier personnage !</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="BOBÉCHOTTE"-->
<sp who="#gustave">
                        <speaker>GUSTAVE.</speaker>
                        <p n="59">
	<s n="1">Moi ?</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="GUSTAVE"-->
<sp who="#bobechotte">
                        <speaker>BOBÉCHOTTE.</speaker>
                        <p n="60">
	<s n="1">D'ailleurs, tout ça, c'est de ma faute et je n'ai que ce que je mérite. </s>
	<s n="2">Si, au lieu de me conduire gentiment avec toi, je m'étais payé ton 24-30 comme les neuf dixièmes des grenouilles que tu as gratifiées de tes faveurs, tu te garderais bien de te payer le mien aujourd'hui. </s>
	<s n="3">C'est toujours le même raisonnement : « Je ne te crains pas ! </s>
	<s n="4">Je t'enquiquine ! » </s>
	<s n="5">Quelle dégoûtation, bon Dieu ! </s>
	<s n="6">Heureusement, il est encore temps.</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@who="BOBÉCHOTTE"-->
<sp who="#gustave">
                        <speaker>GUSTAVE, inquiet.</speaker>
                        <p n="61">
	<s n="1">Hein ? </s>
	<s n="2">Comment ? </s>
	<s n="3">Qu'est-ce que tu dis ? </s>
	<s n="4">Il est encore temps !... </s>
	<s n="5">Temps de quoi ?</s>
</p>
                    </sp><!--@stage="anxious"--><!--@who="GUSTAVE"-->
<sp who="#bobechotte">
                        <speaker>BOBÉCHOTTE.</speaker>
                        <p n="62">
	<s n="1">Je me comprends ; c'est le principal. </s>
